Package com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registry.properties

Interface EntityPropertyRegistry

All Known Subinterfaces:
MutableEntityPropertyRegistry
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultEntityPropertyRegistry, EntityPropertyRegistrySupport, MergingEntityPropertyRegistry
public interface EntityPropertyRegistry
Registry containing a collection of property information. Usually for a particular entity type, although this is not required.
See Also:

  • EntityPropertyRegistryProvider
